:name:
Virtus

:coretxt:
Vampire posses mystical inhuman strength. 
Can be used to acquire bonus dice where applicable, but only up to three.
Can also be used to perform a feat of strength.

:cost:
1 Vigor

:req:
Has used his strength to escape.

:1:
Twise the stregnth of a man. Add bonus die.

:2:
Twise the strength of a horse. Add two bonus dice.

:3:
Twise the strength of a elephant. Add three bonus dice.

:tags:
Vampiric
VampiricStrength
